data.description: Welcome Home! This beautifully updated, move-in ready home is located within the quiet Briery Terrace neighborhood of West Mifflin. The open floor plan consists of a large living room with natural lighting and farmhouse fireplace to a kitchen with gorgeous granite countertops, added cabinet shelving, and stainless steel appliances with a spacious attached dining room. The updated lighting and flooring throughout the main level continues to the upstairs with 3 bedrooms each featuring built-in closets, as well as a newly renovated bathroom! Downstairs you’ll find a finished basement with another updated bathroom and a laundry room with a new washer/dryer. The large 2 car garage leads out back to a newly lighted, fenced in yard that was also regraded/leveled for better use with a large patio for entertaining. Gutters were just updated, with the windows, plumbing, electric, etc. being done the last two years as well.
